Class GeneralAgent

java.lang.Object
  edu.utexas.cs.tamerProject.agents.GeneralAgent
All Implemented Interfaces:
AgentInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
AsynchDPAgent, DPAgent, ExtActionAgentWrap, SarsaLambdaAgent, TamerAgent, TamerRLAgent
public abstract class GeneralAgent
extends java.lang.Object
implements AgentInterface

This abstract class is the ancestor of all other major agent classes in this project. (ExtActionAgentWrap is an exception for now.) Much of the code that is used by the agents is implemented here. Further, the TamerApplet class in the rl-applet codebase assumes that all agents are children of GeneralAgent.
